{"article_id":"GS1X5PKBFP8lLNr7","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Democratic Rep. Eric Swalwell , in an interview Wednesday , would not rule out a new impeachment effort against President Trump over his alleged interference in the criminal case of his former associate Roger Stone .","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"Federal prosecutors on Monday had recommended a sentence of between 87 and 108 months in prison for Stone ' s conviction on seven counts of obstruction , witness tampering and making false statements to Congress on charges","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that stemmed from former Special Counsel Robert Mueller ' s investigation .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"But in a stunning reversal ,","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"as Fox News first reported ,","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"leadership at the Justice Department overruled the prosecutors on the case ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"scaling back the proposed sentence for Stone ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"which immediately led Democrats to accuse Trump of interfering in the process","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"by tweeting about his displeasure with the DOJ .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Trump denies it ,","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"and the case lately has been complicated further by questions over possible juror bias .","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"During an interview with CNN on Wednesday , Swalwell , D-Calif. , was asked","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"whether Democrats would look to launch a new impeachment inquiry on the new controversy .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"\" You know ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"we ' re not going to take our options off the table , \"","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Swalwell , a member of the House Judiciary and Intelligence Committees , told CNN .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"\" We don ' t wake up in the morning","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"wanting to impeach him . \"","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"He added :","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"\" We want to work with him on prescription drugs , background checks , and infrastructure ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"but we ' re not going to let him just torch this democracy","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"because he thinks","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"that he ' s been let off once","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"and we ' re not going to do something about it . \"","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Swalwell ' s comments come","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"as several Democrats on Capitol Hill have demanded investigations","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"-- and even the resignation of Attorney General Bill Barr --","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"after the move","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"to scale back the Stone sentence .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"\" Congress must act immediately","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"to rein in our lawless Attorney General , \"","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"Sen. Elizabeth Warren , D-Mass. , tweeted Wednesday .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"\" Barr should resign","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"or face impeachment . \"","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"Sen. Richard Blumenthal , D-Conn. , also slammed Barr ,","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"he \" ought to be ashamed and embarrassed and resign","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"as a result of this action","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"directly interfering in the independent prosecution of Roger Stone. \"","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"He also said","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"the controversy was yet another example of \" political interference by the president","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"to alter the independent decisions of the Department of Justice . \"","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"House Judiciary Committee Chairman Rep. Jerry Nadler , D-N.Y. , didn ' t answer a question","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"on whether Barr should resign","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"but said :","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"\" I think","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"the behavior is extremely egregious . \"","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"TRUMP DENIES INTERFERING IN ROGER STONE CASE ,","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"STAYS MUM ON POSSIBLE PARDON","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"The latest Democratic fervor comes","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"after four career prosecutors withdrew from the Stone case ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"including one quitting outright ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"after leadership at the Justice Department","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"( DOJ )","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"overruled them .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Senate Democratic Leader Chuck Schumer , D-N.Y. ; Sen. Dianne Feinstein , D-Calif. , and Sen. Kamala Harris , D-Calif. , immediately called for an investigation into Trump 's alleged political intervention into Stone 's sentencing .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Schumer also took to the Senate floor","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"and torched Senate Republicans","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"who acquitted Trump on two articles of impeachment","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"for enabling Trump 's conduct .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"\" Republicans thought","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"the president would learn his lesson , \"","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"Schumer said in a veiled jab at Sen. Susan Collins , R-Maine .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"\" It turned out that the lesson","depth":14},{"id":64,"text":"he learned","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"was not that he went too far","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"-- not that he needed to rein it in .","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"The lesson","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"the president learned","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"was that the Republican Party will not hold him accountable","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"no matter how egregious his behavior .","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"Not now , not ever . \"","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"But Senate Judiciary Committee Chairman Sen. Lindsey Graham was n't too keen on Schumer 's demand for an emergency hearing .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"`` Like I take everything with him [ with ] a grain of salt , ''","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"said Graham , R-S.C .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"Fresh off of weeks of impeachment , Democrats raised similar alarm bells and phrases as during the Ukraine saga ,","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"the Stone matter is another example of political interference , abuse of power","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"and President Trump","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"thinking","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"he 's above the law .","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"Lead impeachment manager Rep. Adam Schiff ripped Trump","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"for trying to influence the judicial system .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"\" It ' s a shocking undermining of the rule of law in this country , \"","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"Schiff said ,","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"it ' s \" an abuse of the powers of his office . \"","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"Another impeachment manager , lawyer and former judge , Rep. Sylvia Garcia , D-Texas , told Fox News :","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"`` This president ' s behavior is just totally out of control .","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"This is one of the most egregious things","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"that I ' ve ever seen . ''","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"She stopped short of calling for Barr 's resignation","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"but said :","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"`` We ca n't sit back","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"and not do something .","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"The question is what . ''","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"She ticked off the oversight tools","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"House Democrats still have .","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"`` It ' s hearings .","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"It 's investigation .","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"It 's litigation .","depth":15},{"id":101,"text":"It 's subpoenas .","depth":16},{"id":102,"text":"It 's contempt .","depth":16},{"id":103,"text":"It 's all the same ones","depth":15},{"id":104,"text":"we 've always had ,","depth":15},{"id":105,"text":"but it 's a question","depth":15},{"id":106,"text":"of making sure","depth":16},{"id":107,"text":"that we 're strategic in what we do , ''","depth":16},{"id":108,"text":"she said .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"However , Trump on Wednesday denied interfering in Stone ' s criminal case ,","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"while declining to say","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"whether he ' d consider a pardon for the GOP political operative .","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"\" The fact is that Roger Stone was treated horribly","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"and so were many other people , \"","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"Trump said .","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"\" Their lives were destroyed . \"","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"\" I want to thank the Justice Department","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"-- and I didn ' t speak to them , by the way --","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"they saw a nine-year sentence ...","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"nine years for something","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"nobody can even define what he did , \"","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"Trump continued .","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"\" They put a man in jail ,","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"destroy his life , his family , his wife . \"","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"He added :","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"\" Roger Stone --","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"nobody even knows","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"what he did ...","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"Frankly , they ought to apologize to a lot of people","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"whose lives","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"they ' ve ruined . \"","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"Stone is scheduled to be sentenced by Judge Amy Berman Jackson on Feb. 20 .","depth":3},{"id":132,"text":"Earlier this month , after a weeks-long Senate trial , the president was acquitted on charges of abuse of power and obstruction of Congress in connection to his pressure campaign on Ukraine","depth":3},{"id":133,"text":"to investigate Democrats ."